<taxonomicNameLabel pageId="23" pageNumber="112">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 13" captionStartId="F13" captionText="Figure 13. Pachyptera linearis. A Flowering branch B Interpetiolar region with ENFs and prophylls of axillary buds 3 - seriated, flattened and ensiform C Branchlets with terminal leaflet replaced by trifid tendril (leaflet fells) D Trifid tentril E Flower F Calyx external view G Open flower showing the androecium with anthers united H Stamen with villous and curved thecae I Gynoecium J Ovary surface pubescent (J. J. Wurdack 41357, K) K Fruit flattened, with an inconspicuous longitudinal midline L Seeds wingless (P. Stevenson 403, MO)." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.92.20987.figure13" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/180450" pageId="23" pageNumber="112">Fig. 13</figureCitation>
